headline: ETHISPHERE Names Western Digital as One of the 2025 World’s Most Ethical Companies® for the Seventh Time
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., March 11, 2025--Western Digital (Nasdaq: WDC) has received the 2025 World’s Most Ethical Companies® recognition by Ethisphere, a global leader in defining and advancing the standards of ethical business practices.
